		<div class="post" id="post-5322">
			<h2><a href="http://depletedcranium.com/why-you-cant-build-a-bomb-from-spent-fuel/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link: Why You Can&#8217;t Build a Bomb From Spent Fuel">Why You Can&#8217;t Build a Bomb From Spent Fuel</a></h2>


<small>February 20th, 2010 <!-- by drbuzz0 --></small>
<br><br>

<table border="0" width="620" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" id="social">
