			<div class="quoter-wrap">
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href="http://depletedcranium.com/why-you-cant-build-a-bomb-from-spent-fuel/#comment-23688"><b>Silverthorn said:</b></a></p>
